{"tid":469761,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"（有感）叫你阿 廢青90後考DSE個啲全部同我入黎","createTime":"2017-11-15T15:44:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T22:16:40.000Z","uid":148608,"like":131,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5f681c8a638f17955b95021734db7d3969a93b7a","tid":469761,"uid":148608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:44:45.000Z","msg":"話說又要交assignment, 早幾星期先chur完mid term.<br />\n諗返起中學唔知邊條友講話咩入到U唔撚駛温書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔駛温噤少<br />\n真係辛9苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就係噤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我啲中學情懷又出晒黎.<br />\n諗住去個自修室大戰30回合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知經過比我見到有中學生着件噤嘅衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/15/233131_d0242c06c573324af69f1f1ed05632a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F15%2F233131_d0242c06c573324af69f1f1ed05632a3.jpg&h=b7dc8f13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後我就自己係張濕9自修室枱到, 開始諗嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冷氣一樣噤凍, 啲𡃁仔一樣温書, 啲阿叔一樣瞓覺,<br />\n我又係坐左係到, 唔同嘅純粹係我讀緊u (抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )做緊assignment噤<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚掛住中學<br />\n<br />\n以前返學最型最多咪田X辰恤衫加條窄腳西褲<br />\n(豐X順個啲真係收皮)<br />\n宜家返學又要諗着咩衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔知邊條友認得我上星期又係呢set outfit<br />\n又有女同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係煩<br />\n<br />\n中學返學又驚遲到, 難得真係遲到就去茶記食早餐.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後就大牌返課室比同學屌話走堂走交功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就開始諗lunch食乜嘢<br />\n然後放學就補習<br />\n<br />\n宜家miss左930個場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就基本喇<br />\n上完堂就返hall打機, hea, 同做deadline fighter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲晚聚係開心嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過如果common room啲人係中學同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我會更加開心姐<br />\n<br />\n好掛住以前去灣仔學界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好掛住放學練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好掛住啲老師同同學...好掛着校服拍拖嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nprofessor采你都有味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nhibye friend周圍都係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大學係開心係自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過中學時光真係取代唔到<br />\n<br />\n上年準備DSE呢一年, 最痛苦但又最難忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLast day啲人喊到豬西噤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家望住寫滿野嘅校服 真係好有feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後到真係study leave個排, 日日都一樣:<br />\n雀巢咖啡-&gt;自修室-&gt;葡萄適-&gt;返歸<br />\n啲past paper比我做到狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n辛苦到傻撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n考説話收到個條on9題目<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要第一日考<br />\n乜撚野獎勵原則排優次? 心諗乜料?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後考都core每一晚都瞓唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放榜個日收到張紙冇乜話好感動, 感觸就真.<br />\n眼見啲同學有啲好失望, 有啲喜出望外.<br />\n<br />\n望返轉頭6年讀嘅書就係用係呢幾個鐘嘅卷到<br />\n就係個幾個數字授權你資格入咩科<br />\n你入咩科決定你搵咩工<br />\n咩工決定你食屎定食飯<br />\n但係分數背後嘅代價呢？<br />\n<br />\n有人冇左青春<br />\n有人冇左製造回憶嘅機會<br />\n有人冇左段感情(姐係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n屌...<br />\n<br />\n都希望藉呢個機會同所有大學/大專院校<br />\n上年考唔好要retake嘅巴絲打, 2018 dse<br />\n加油喇屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然dse係萬惡根源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都係round up全個中學時光嘅句號<br />\n<br />\n完。<br />\n<br />\n所以話 大家讀緊嘅學位係用血淚換返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 珍而重之<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好掛住中學但DSE我屌你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好撚鍾意DSE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我入到U冇女追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我好樣衰<br />\n<br />\n利申：聽日唔check attendance準時走lecture <br />\nbtw: 有冇人知可以係邊到買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8143befce1aa15b9bd8aefa8109b2236730f3ca9","tid":469761,"uid":60115,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T15:47:35.000Z","msg":"傻仔先咁努力考dse<br />\n醒目仔就梗係讀asso輕鬆走後門入三大"},{"pid":"fb3e3284ae8fd4c3937ee0a175e28b69d324a1aa","tid":469761,"uid":61965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:23:54.000Z","msg":"今日起身自動走左堂0830<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f98f2e3ebd901acee62ed04719bb34dd50c4242","tid":469761,"uid":43856,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:41:12.000Z","msg":"本來都好地地我準備㩒正皮嘅<br />\n屌你老母投乜撚野票呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74aa141fedc5b82878838859f9f2828f6aab855","tid":469761,"uid":83915,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T21:29:24.000Z","msg":"2016 DSE 完全同感<br />\n<br />\n唯一唔同既係而家我係外國讀緊...仲要呢一年半來只係返過香港一次。對我黎講係香港既回憶，就係日頭係灣修溫DSE, 夜晚係屋企附近既咖啡店溫到10 點再返屋企既時光。<br />\n<br />\n而家係呢邊生活模式唔同左好多，所以一諗返起過去，就覺得呢一切都好不可思議、好遙遠，但同時好真實。<br />\n<br />\n多謝你樓主 睇到呢個post 令我又再一次諗起好好好回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d349a15d7b7f4320dd46e83c2265b85ee45680","tid":469761,"uid":136982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T11:58:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/disclaimer898/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdisclaimer898%2F&d=wRYxnbutjtFT%2FkEIN6DJLL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=07c70d13\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/disclaimer898/</a><br />\n個logo一樣 唔知係咪條友整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00738539bc4fc3078ba182256d72db7f7c73a6b","tid":469761,"uid":69754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T16:48:33.000Z","msg":"個post唔錯<br />\n但可唔可以唔好投票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ae580d8046b5119dd4845733ff577437673de0b","tid":469761,"uid":42764,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T16:58:38.000Z","msg":"除左中文通識呢啲垃圾之外，其實DSE科算易<br />\n尤其自己會睇返AL pp，做下外國試題，廿幾年前會考題，你就知呢廿年越出越淺，學既野越來越少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 : 2015DSE"},{"pid":"f521fce516f86c5d1df0d2b6b5dc08827764e514","tid":469761,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T02:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43bc96601f23cd499be43fc9d6bae5e076835cbd","tid":469761,"uid":148608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/disclaimer898/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fdisclaimer898%2F&d=wRYxnb